\binom n0\left(\frac{p-1}{p}\right)^n+\binom n1\left(\frac{p-1}{p}\right)^{n-1}\frac1p=\left(1-\frac1p\right)^{n-1}\left(1+\frac{n-1}p\right)\;.
p_n=\prod_p\left(1-\frac1p\right)^{n-1}\left(1+\frac{n-1}p\right)\;.
