p_{n+1}=\prod_p\left(1-\frac1p\right)^n\left(1+\frac np\right)=\prod_p\left(1-\frac1{p^2}\right)^n\frac{1+\frac np}{\left(1+\frac 1p\right)^n}=\zeta(2)^{-n} \prod_p\frac{1+\frac np}{\left(1+\frac 1p\right)^n}\;,
